description._content: Image Description: This dock is near the Yaquina Oyster Laboratory and the photo was used in the 1939 "A progress report of investigations for the native oyster in Yaquina Bay, Oregon" by R. E. Dimick and Jay Long (Figure 10). Original Collection: Agricultural Experiment Station Records Item Number: RG25 You can find this image by searching for the item number by clicking here.
